<p>The Uintah Basin's economy is driven by energy, infrastructure, and public land management. Our extended-stay guests reflect that — the same industries that keep Vernal working are the ones that fill our rooms week after week. We understand rotating schedules, early morning departures, late-night arrivals, and the need for a room that's more than just a bed.</p>
<ul class="feat-list">
 <li>Oil and gas — drilling, completion, and production crews</li>
 <li>Pipeline construction and maintenance teams</li>
 <li>Utility and power line contractors</li>
 <li>BLM, Forest Service, and government field staff</li>
